      "*": "<div class=\"mw-parser-output\"><p><b><a href=\"/Main_Page\" title=\"Main Page\">Home</a> * <a href=\"/Tournaments_and_Matches\" title=\"Tournaments and Matches\">Tournaments</a> * <a href=\"/World_Computer_Chess_Championship\" title=\"World Computer Chess Championship\">World Computer Chess Championship</a> * 1st WCCC Stockholm 1974</b>\n</p><p><b><a href=\"/WCCC_1977\" title=\"WCCC 1977\">Next &gt;</a></b>\n</p>\n <div class=\"thumb tright\"><div class=\"thumbinner\" style=\"width:257px;\"><a href=\"/File:Birger_jarl_(Forss%C3%A9n).jpg\" class=\"image\"><img alt=\"\" src=\"https://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/d/d5/Birger_jarl_%28Forss%C3%A9n%29.jpg\" width=\"255\" height=\"353\" class=\"thumbimage\" /></a>  <div class=\"thumbcaption\"><div class=\"magnify\"><a href=\"/File:Birger_jarl_(Forss%C3%A9n).jpg\" class=\"internal\" title=\"Enlarge\"></a></div><a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Birger_Jarl\">Birger Jarl</a> <sup id=\"cite_ref-1\" class=\"reference\"><a href=\"#cite_note-1\">&#91;1&#93;</a></sup></div></div></div>\n<p>The <b>First World Computer Chess Championship</b> took place from August 5 to August 8, <a href=\"/Timeline#1974\" title=\"Timeline\">1974</a>, in <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Birger_Jarl#Late_life\">Hotel Birger-Jarl</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Stockholm\">Stockholm</a>, <a rel=\"nofollow\" class=\"external text\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Sweden\">Sweden</a> under the auspices of <a href=\"/IFIP\" title=\"IFIP\">IFIP</a>. It was a four round swiss tournament with 13 participants. <a href=\"/Kaissa\" title=\"Kaissa\">Kaissa</a> was the sole winner with 4 out of 4. \n</p>\n<div id=\"toc\" class=\"toc\"><div class=\"toctitle\"><h2>Contents</h2></div>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-1\"><a href=\"#Final_Standing\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Final Standing</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-2\"><a href=\"#Participants\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Participants</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-3\"><a href=\"#Photos_.26_Games\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Photos &amp; Games</span></a>\n<ul>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-4\"><a href=\"#Chess_4.0_-_Ribbit\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.1</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Chess 4.0 - Ribbit</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-5\"><a href=\"#Tech_2_-_Kaissa\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.2</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Tech 2 - Kaissa</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-2 tocsection-6\"><a href=\"#CHAOS_-_Chess_4.0\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">3.3</span> <span class=\"toctext\">CHAOS - Chess 4.0</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-7\"><a href=\"#Quotes\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">4</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Quotes</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-8\"><a href=\"#See_also\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">5</span> <span class=\"toctext\">See also</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-9\"><a href=\"#Publications\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">6</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Publications</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-10\"><a href=\"#Forum_Post\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">7</span> <span class=\"toctext\">Forum Post</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-11\"><a href=\"#External_Links\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">8</span> <span class=\"toctext\">External Links</span></a></li>\n<li class=\"toclevel-1 tocsection-12\"><a href=\"#References\"><span class=\"tocnumber\">9</span> <span class=\"toctext\">References</span></a></li>\n</ul>\n</div>\n\n<h1><span class=\"mw-headline\" id=\"Final_Standing\">Final Standing</span><span class=\"mw-editsection\"><span class=\"mw-editsection-bracket\">[</span><a href=\"/index.php?title=WCCC_1974&amp;action=edit&a